<h4>Is it expensive to host a trainee?</h4>

<p>On the contrary! The program is completely free for the host company AND you can save on
payroll taxes and insurance. All participants are exempt from Social Security (FICA), Medicare
and Federal Unemployment Tax (FUTA) and they already come with their own travel insurance
for the whole duration of the program.</p>

